title: Ebro In The Morning - Rest In Peace Young Dolph + Rosenberg's Thanksgiving Bars
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 11/18.

Ebro and the crew discuss the death of Young Dolph (43), the Flashing Lights reports shine light on the days biggest news and Rosenberg drops some brand new Thanksgiving Bars (58).
